{"tid":1486790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何走下去?  818之後","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:39.000Z","uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31d7eeaf181e26a250c98cba3b49940661782915","tid":1486790,"uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">818 維園龐龎170萬+，甚至270萬人集會，<br />\n在10小時內基本上看不到警察的情況下，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>市民自覺和平散去！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果社會及市民是在一個混亂不受控制、不理智的狀況，818集會就不可能又一次顯示了支持民主自由的香港人的和平理性質素。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">市民對政府的不滿沒有減退，對政府的不信任沒有改善。</span></span></strong><br />\n818和平集會是市民給予政府改善關係、真正行動回應巿民及示威者訴求的又一次機會！<br />\n<br />\n昨晚政府連續對大氣電波發了六份新聞稿，但沒有一份回應市民五個訴求中的任何一個。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府對逃犯修例要求完全撤回的訴求隻字未提，對成立獨立調查會的要求視若無睹！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請政府珍惜市民及示威者為她爭取修補社會撕裂機會的心血！<br />\n政府還要多少日去有效回應訴求？1天、5天？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心血會亁，但市民的不信任及憤怒只會增添，不會自然退卻！不要妄想！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">懇求政府改過，在走上不歸路之前，沒有人知道這是不是最後的一次機會！</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n#####################################################<br />\n参考POSTS:<br />\n打開缺口 - 機場行動: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486709/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486709/page/1</a><br />\n［ 8 2 4 召 集 ］ 機 場 交 通 壓 力 測 試 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1483611\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1483611</a><br />\n#####################################################"},{"pid":"ffbba005110eda2dc3d26fcea9da5e86017cd560","tid":1486790,"uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73b6c7ce86efd79b81a75fb1e5db99e572ff921b","tid":1486790,"uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"387c185666f773d7a5e19fb8c406975b58baa8c2","tid":1486790,"uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168f24308e9a97855b5c48e944994b62091bdd71","tid":1486790,"uid":276386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}